lass=\"theme-card relative flex w-full flex-col rounded-2xl border p-5 transition sm:p-6\"><h3><a href=\"/blog/portfolio-site-2\"><span class=\"absolute inset-0 rounded-2xl\"></span><svg data-prefix=\"fas\" data-icon=\"code\" class=\"svg-inline--fa fa-code text-[var(--theme-text-muted)] fa-lg\" role=\"img\" viewBox=\"0 0 576 512\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M360.8 1.2c-17-4.9-34.7 5-39.6 22l-128 448c-4.9 17 5 34.7 22 39.6s34.7-5 39.6-22l128-448c4.9-17-5-34.7-22-39.6zm64.6 136.1c-12.5 12.5-12.5 32.8 0 45.3l73.4 73.4-73.4 73.4c-12.5 12.5-12.5 32.8 0 45.3s32.8 12.5 45.3 0l96-96c12.5-12.5 12.5-32.8 0-45.3l-96-96c-12.5-12.5-32.8-12.5-45.3 0zm-274.7 0c-12.5-12.5-32.8-12.5-45.3 0l-96 96c-12.5 12.5-12.5 32.8 0 45.3l96 96c12.5 12.5 32.8 12.5 45.3 0s12.5-32.8 0-45.3L77.3 256 150.6 182.6c12.5-12.5 12.5-32.8 0-45.3z\"></path></svg></a></h3><p class=\"mt-4 flex gap-x-2 text-xs text-[var(--theme-text-muted)]\"><time dateTime=\"2025\" class=\"font-semibold text-[var(--theme-text-primary)]\">2025</time><span class=\"text-[var(--theme-text-muted)]\" aria-hidden=\"true\">/</span><span>Article</span></p><p class=\"mt-3 font-display text-base font-semibold text-[var(--theme-text-primary)]\">Portfolio Site Rebuild — Part 2: Building the Core</p><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm text-[var(--theme-text-secondary)]\">Setting up the Next.js project, building the component library, wiring up MDX with Zod validation, and designing the homepage layout.</p></article></div><div class=\"flex\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><article class=\"theme-card relative flex w-full flex-col rounded-2xl border p-5 transition sm:p-6\"><h3><a href=\"/blog/portfolio-site-1\"><span class=\"absolute inset-0 rounded-2xl\"></span><svg data-prefix=\"fas\" data-icon=\"code\" class=\"svg-inline--fa fa-code text-[var(--theme-text-muted)] fa-lg\" role=\"img\" viewBox=\"0 0 576 512\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M360.8 1.2c-17-4.9-34.7 5-39.6 22l-128 448c-4.9 17 5 